Heatmap layer

The heatmap layer displays observations distribution as a heatmap overlay.

import polars as pl
from pylifemap import Lifemap

# Load iucn dataset
iucn = pl.read_csv(
    "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/juba/pylifemap/main/data/iucn.csv"
)

(
    Lifemap(iucn)
    .layer_heatmap(opacity=0.5)
    .show()
)

For a detailed list of layer_heatmap arguments you can take a look at its documentation.
